.TH "snd_hdac_stream_timecounter_init" 9 "snd_hdac_stream_timecounter_init" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hdac_stream_timecounter_init \- initialize time counter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" snd_hdac_stream_timecounter_init
.BI "(struct hdac_stream *azx_dev "  ","
.BI "unsigned int streams "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "azx_dev" 12
HD-audio core stream (master stream)
.IP "streams" 12
bit flags of streams to set up
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the time counter of streams marked by the bit flags (each
bit corresponds to the stream index).
The trigger timestamp of PCM substream assigned to the given stream is
updated accordingly, too.
